Jardine Lloyd Thompson Logo Jardine Lloyd Thompson Group, also known as JLT Group or simply JLT, is a British multinational corporation that has its headquarters in London, England. It provides insurance, reinsurance, employment benefits advice and brokerage services. It was a constituent of the FTSE 250 Index until it was acquired by Marsh & McLennan Companies in April 2019.
